debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: I was asked to determine which of two shapes I thought would get me more points in the first part. There were a couple practice runs and then I had an actual trial. Then I was asked to make the choice on whether a number was > or < 153 or if a letter was closer to a or z (both letter and number appearing at the same time).  I then was timed doing those things (not on a timer I could see but the speed with which I put my answer was taken into account for my points total).
